script:
1). I thought you were going to meet with Tom today.
I haven't met Tom.
I wasn't meeting him.
I was, but he's out sick. 
2). How soon can you finish taking inventory?
In about an hour. 
I will take it soon.
I'm not done yet.
3). She hasn't been here before, has she?
I don't believe she has. 
I haven't been.
No, she hadn't.
